dct_title_s: A general chart exhibiting the discoveries made by Captn. James Cook in this and his two preceeding voyages : with tracks of the ships under his command
dct_description_sm: "Engrav'd for Cook's Voyage, Octavo Edition." From: Captain Cook's third and last voyage to the Pacific Ocean. London : Printed for J. Fielding and J. Stockdale ... , [1785] Lieutenant Henry Roberts compiled a composite chart of Cook's three voyages for the official account published in 1784. cf. Tooley's dictionary of mapmakers.
